stanford.karel

Class HeadlessKarel

  • java.lang.Object
    • stanford.karel.HeadlessKarel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProgramInterface, Runnable, KarelInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HeadlessSuperKarel

    public class HeadlessKarel
extends Object
    A version of a Karel superclass that doesn't crash when run in headless (non-graphical) mode.
